{"tid":1017201,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港明年12月起終止模擬電視廣播 料16萬戶獲資助換電視","createTime":"2019-02-11T09:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T13:34:45.000Z","uid":131616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dd847c77b681786f83f22d02efc0c7b7d4df4197","tid":1017201,"uid":131616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"港府原定於2012年底，全面取消俗稱「雪花」電視的模擬電視廣播，騰出頻譜，供高增值的流動電訊服務或未來的電視台使用，惟計劃一再押後，今午（11日）終宣佈由明年12月起，終止模擬電視廣播。商務及經濟發展局初步建議，18萬受影響的模擬電視住戶，可申請「關愛基金」撥款，購置數碼電視或機頂盒，預計約有16萬戶合資格申請。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190211/59246761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59246761&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1wbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=e264085a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59246761&h=b0c8925f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190211/59246761</a>"},{"pid":"a7da1b036d07d08ac1be94029fc330dc6074b123","tid":1017201,"uid":198165,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"娛樂性質都可以申請關愛基金，不撚知所謂"},{"pid":"4754df9b2d67b07b37710d06bd91045b978fd680","tid":1017201,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"有無人屋企仲睇緊模擬?WHY?"},{"pid":"bc2c67c4b3c265f04756962da492a63b7dcb0393","tid":1017201,"uid":33104,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"新年前先見有人掉左部，早知拎左佢等申請資助啦，交完